caption.text:
Got tagged by @rinintahaha on this #20factsaboutme challenge. So here's the 20 facts you might know and not know about me:
1. Kalo ngomong selalu pake "aku-kamu".
2. A Scorpion, A type, and got phlegmatic-melancholic on a personality test.
3. Paling males kalo disuruh belajar sama beresin kamar.
4. Alasan utama masuk aksel waktu di interview: males sekolah kelamaan dan pengen cepet2 sekolah gambar.
5. The first time I slept during a class was when I was still in kindergarten.
6. I think cats are cute but I'm scared of them.
7. I really like Kyary Pamyu Pamyu because she's so kawaii with her absurdity but I'm not a fan of her music.
8. MY FAVORITE NUMBAH!!
9. My favorite colors are black, white, and grey. This might be the reason why my life has been so colorless...
10. I love to eat :9
11. Suka dikira kembaran sama kakak sendiri...
12. "Kamu kalo nangis kecantikan kamu bertambah" - @jelitanden . Okedeh bu...
13. I used be a soprano, and then turned into mezzo-soprano, but now I'm an alto voice on the choir team.
14. I like Amy Lee's and Christina Aguilera's voice. They're so amazing!
15. I listen mostly to rock, musicals, and some instrumental and classical music.
16. I tend to hide my feelings so often because I feel so uneasy to tell people about it.
17. I dreamed of becoming an architect when I was on the 3rd grade.
18. I love to sing when I take a shower. (who doesn't?)
19. I love hugging people!
20. I'm so curious about my future.
And that's all! I tag @saffiralindra @azkazafira @adinafairuz @strikefreedom_ to do this challenge, though it's up to you if you wanna do this or not. K then, see you later ~ !
